      <title>由於某些產品的需求降溫，舒適達製造商 Haleon 銷售不溫不火</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/haleons-first-quarter-revenue-misses-expectations-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消費者保健公司 Haleon 週三公佈的第一季營收略低於市場預期，原因是美國零售商去庫存以及去年激增後對其部分藥品的需求降溫導致銷量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/haleons-first-quarter-revenue-misses-expectations-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 07:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
