      <title>阿斯頓馬丁季度虧損超出預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-posts-bigger-than-expected-quarterly-loss-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯頓馬丁週三公佈的第一季稅前虧損超出預期，因為這家英國豪華汽車製造商生產的汽車數量較少，現金消耗量也高於分析師預期，導致該公司股價下跌 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-posts-bigger-than-expected-quarterly-loss-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 06:23:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
